Pong Clone for more than 2 players with network support

We will use the Lightweight Java Game Library (LWJGL) for this project.
LWJGL project site ->	http://lwjgl.org/

##Milestones##
[X]	prototype 2 player offline
[ ]	more than 2 players support
[X]	network support server/client
[ ]	applet/browser support
